},"13":{"Type":"Standard","SubType":"","Description":"relevant vienna","ID":"BL_cvbYzHUQA9GUQw6","BlockElements":[{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID129"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID56"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID218"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID57"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID58"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID59"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID60"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID98"}],"Options":{"BlockLocking":false,"RandomizeQuestions":"Advanced","Randomization":{"Advanced":{"FixedOrder":["QID129","QID56","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}"],"RandomizeAll":["QID57","QID58","QID59","QID60","QID98","QID218"],"RandomSubSet":[],"Undisplayed":[],"TotalRandSubset":0,"QuestionsPerPage":0},"EvenPresentation":false},"BlockVisibility":"Expanded","Looping":"Static","LoopingOptions":{"Static":{"1":{"1":"I learned that suspicious activity should be looked into and investigated right away, especially if someone has their suspicions, as these could turn out to be true."},"2":{"1":"I learnt that as people we do not believe something until there is proven theory of it being dangerous or making an impact in our lives."},"3":{"1":"There was a doctor which proposed a theory that not washing hands is leading to the increased risk of disease and ailments. He also proposed this theory to the doctors but they didn't like it and it wasn't approved. It was only after the Germ Theory, that the doctors started associating the germ theory with the given theory and started incorporating the procedure of \"washing hands\". It gave me the insight that even before the Germ Theory, there was someone who found the cause of increased risk of ailments, but only after a \"theory\", the \"compelling evidence\" was accepted."},"4":{"1":"theory that explains real life experience is valuable to changing public perception. Examples are useful."}},"Randomization":"Subset","TotalRandSubset":"1"}}},"29":{"Type":"Standard","SubType":"","Description":"message vienna","ID":"BL_0VxvpfNdVJZB9Hg","BlockElements":[{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID210"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID211"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID219"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID212"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID213"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID214"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID215"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID216"}],"Options":{"BlockLocking":false,"RandomizeQuestions":"Advanced","Randomization":{"Advanced":{"FixedOrder":["QID210","QID211","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}"],"RandomizeAll":["QID212","QID213","QID214","QID215","QID216","QID219"],"RandomSubSet":[],"Undisplayed":[],"TotalRandSubset":0,"QuestionsPerPage":0},"EvenPresentation":false},"BlockVisibility":"Collapsed","Looping":"Static","LoopingOptions":{"Static":{"1":{"1":"Before this lesson I did not give much thought into how important a theory is, I only thought that the evidence on its own was the only thing important, now I see that differently."},"2":{"1":"you always need a theory to base off evidence"},"3":{"1":"That no matter how good your evidence and aguement is, some people will not believe it just because they need a good theory to back it up"},"4":{"1":"I learnt that people not only require strong evidence but some underlying theory before they change their minds about something."},"5":{"1":"No matter how the evidence is put forward some people will like to hear the theory version of the lesson rather than the visual evidence presented to them "},"6":{"1":"it makes peoples minds to be in a faster state"},"7":{"1":"Its saying that I can't just use hard data, facts, or \"evidence\" to convince somebody of something - explaining how something works and the \"theory\" behind it can give them the insight to come to their own realization of the truth."}},"Randomization":"Subset","TotalRandSubset":"1"}}},"30":{"Type":"Standard","SubType":"","Description":"relevant merrick","ID":"BL_czJd0nGhjkFTKp8","BlockElements":[{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID220"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID221"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID222"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID223"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID224"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID225"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID226"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID227"}],"Options":{"BlockLocking":false,"RandomizeQuestions":"Advanced","Randomization":{"Advanced":{"FixedOrder":["QID220","QID221","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}"],"RandomizeAll":["QID223","QID224","QID225","QID226","QID227","QID222"],"RandomSubSet":[],"Undisplayed":[],"TotalRandSubset":0,"QuestionsPerPage":0},"EvenPresentation":false},"BlockVisibility":"Expanded","Looping":"Static","LoopingOptions":{"Static":{"1":{"1":"PET FOOD THAT HELPS PETS TO HAVE LESS PLAQUE , THE CUSTOMERS WANTED FOOD THAT HELP WITH FRESH BREATH INSTEAD. THIS PRODUCT WAS CONSIDER A FAILED PRODUCT "},"2":{"1":"I learnt the importance of the description of a product is vital to drive up sales and which dog food is healthy for dogs to reduce plague."},"3":{"1":"The second example of a lesson was far better - it gave a specific example of the wording that could cause a difference in perspective for customers. As well, it detailed the specific outcome of the discrepancy in matching customers expectations in how a product was presented. "},"4":{"1":"A small difference can have a huge impact. No matter how similar you think things are, they are not identical and that change can cause enormous changes."}},"Randomization":"Subset","TotalRandSubset":"1"}}},"31":{"Type":"Standard","SubType":"","Description":"message merrick","ID":"BL_89eofa2kkpuokBw","BlockElements":[{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID228"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID229"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID230"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID231"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID232"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID233"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID234"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID235"}],"Options":{"BlockLocking":false,"RandomizeQuestions":"Advanced","Randomization":{"Advanced":{"FixedOrder":["QID228","QID229","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}"],"RandomizeAll":["QID231","QID232","QID233","QID234","QID235","QID230"],"RandomSubSet":[],"Undisplayed":[],"TotalRandSubset":0,"QuestionsPerPage":0},"EvenPresentation":false},"BlockVisibility":"Collapsed","Looping":"Static","LoopingOptions":{"Static":{"1":{"1":"it showed me that a proper marketing can build a business "},"2":{"1":"If i wish to sell a product I'll have to apply as much attention as possible in the wording of my product description and write something that matches as much as possible the product and potential customers, as even the simplest wrong word can make an impactful difference in sales."},"3":{"1":"Description are meant to give full information omitting or changing certain information can make people believe the product is not the same"},"4":{"1":"The changes in text description of product can change sales"},"5":{"1":"I learned that even slight details in the description of a product, such as slightly different wording, can affect people's decision to buy a product, and therefore sales."},"6":{"1":"Although the content was short and did not provide specific examples of what these changes to product descriptions were, the overall insight into the tactic and strategy of the concept was very interesting to me. It compelled me to do further research."},"7":{"1":"Changing a product's valeu can easily increase  its market sales and people's perspective on how they view the product."}},"Randomization":"Subset","TotalRandSubset":"1"}}},"33":{"Type":"Standard","SubType":"","Description":"case\/message anchoring module","ID":"B