"Randomization":{"Advanced":{"FixedOrder":["QID242","QID243","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}"],"RandomizeAll":["QID245","QID246","QID247","QID248","QID249","QID244"],"RandomSubSet":[],"Undisplayed":[],"TotalRandSubset":0,"QuestionsPerPage":0},"EvenPresentation":false},"BlockVisibility":"Expanded","Looping":"Static","LoopingOptions":{"Static":{"1":{"1":"It challenges your knowledge on medical situations, and says you shouldn't always jump to conclusions."},"2":{"1":"Life can be ruthless and unfair. No matter how right you may think you are, or if you have all the evidence and facts proving your statements, people will only believe a certain truth if it's close enough to their reality."},"3":{"1":"A well thought through article or learning material will have a greater impact than something mundane and not very targeted"},"4":{"1":"Sometimes handing out evidence or sharing your testimonies with people does not always convince them"}},"Randomization":"Subset","TotalRandSubset":"1"}}},"35":{"Type":"Standard","SubType":"","Description":"irrelevant merrick","ID":"BL_7OFhpVrbMJzXo7s","BlockElements":[{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID250"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID251"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID252"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID253"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID254"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID255"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID256"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID257"}],"Options":{"BlockLocking":false,"RandomizeQuestions":"Advanced","Randomization":{"Advanced":{"FixedOrder":["QID250","QID251","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}"],"RandomizeAll":["QID253","QID254","QID255","QID256","QID257","QID252"],"RandomSubSet":[],"Undisplayed":[],"TotalRandSubset":0,"QuestionsPerPage":0},"EvenPresentation":false},"BlockVisibility":"Expanded","Looping":"Static","LoopingOptions":{"Static":{"1":{"1":"In the first lesson, I learned that you only need to make subtle changes to a product description to affect sales considerably. In the second lesson, I learned about a man named Merrick (?) who developed a pet food that promoted dental care in the animals that ate it. Unfortunately, it didn't do very well, despite the fact that Merrick was rumoured to do personal taste tests of all his products."},"2":{"1":"The CEO that developed the pet food used a description for the food that did not promote sales of the product, although he judged the food as good enough for his pets, it still did not sell. Using a compelling description on an item will increase sales, a basic description will not attract buyers"},"3":{"1":"The description that was given for the product was centered on the CEO thinking highly of their own product instead of focusing on the customer which is not what the business should aim for this could have resulted in the decrease in sales."}},"Randomization":"Subset","TotalRandSubset":"1"}}},"36":{"Type":"Standard","SubType":"","Description":"message blockbuster","ID":"BL_ekD9DiyvBIE3rq6","BlockElements":[{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID258"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID259"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID260"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID261"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID262"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID263"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID264"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID265"}],"Options":{"BlockLocking":false,"RandomizeQuestions":"Advanced","Randomization":{"Advanced":{"FixedOrder":["QID258","QID259","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}"],"RandomizeAll":["QID261","QID262","QID263","QID264","QID265","QID260"],"RandomSubSet":[],"Undisplayed":[],"TotalRandSubset":0,"QuestionsPerPage":0},"EvenPresentation":false},"BlockVisibility":"Expanded","Looping":"Static","LoopingOptions":{"Static":{"1":{"1":"I have understood that sometimes you have to get along with the trending industries so as to be equipped with knowledge of whats happening and also get an opportunity for employment."},"2":{"1":"If you don't watch and learn from the trends of people spending money and styles and such, you can miss out on money"},"3":{"1":"Society and the economy change, in order to do well in a business one must be willing to conform and change according to what is new and popular. Products, services, etc. must not remain stagnant otherwise opportunities for business growth will be lost."},"4":{"1":"I have learned that in business you need to consider all the aspects to make your business a success."},"5":{"1":"For business growth and success, it is important to keep track of emerging trends and technologies and try to adapt to them"},"6":{"1":"There's really a great valuable information I got from what I read."},"7":{"1":"It is important to know relevant trends or issues that can affect the market "}},"Randomization":"Subset","TotalRandSubset":"1"}}},"37":{"Type":"Standard","SubType":"","Description":"irrelevant blockbuster","ID":"BL_82rFRB3GyCCPW3Y","BlockElements":[{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID266"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID267"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID268"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID269"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID270"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID271"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID272"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID273"}],"Options":{"BlockLocking":false,"RandomizeQuestions":"Advanced","Randomization":{"Advanced":{"FixedOrder":["QID266","QID267","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}"],"RandomizeAll":["QID269","QID270","QID271","QID272","QID273","QID268"],"RandomSubSet":[],"Undisplayed":[],"TotalRandSubset":0,"QuestionsPerPage":0},"EvenPresentation":false},"BlockVisibility":"Expanded","Looping":"Static","LoopingOptions":{"Static":{"1":{"1":"It doesn't matter what class you give or lecture you give or attend, if the words of the person you are listening to is impactful it will be meaningful and memorable. It needs to speak either to your profession or to your person and it needs to feel profound for you to remember the lesson and for you to take it with you and remember it. Also knowing facts like who the person is and especially someone with meaning behind them carries more impact as well."},"2":{"1":"Keep riding your wave and find your balance "},"3":{"1":"You must always be able to predict the changes of trends in every industry if you want your business to succeed.  "},"4":{"1":"It does not matter hw many times you fall you will have to rise again"}},"Randomization":"Subset","TotalRandSubset":"1"}}},"38":{"Type":"Standard","SubType":"","Description":"relevant blockbuster","ID":"BL_9H5hkRas7a7r9K6","BlockElements":[{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID274"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID275"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID276"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID277"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID278"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID279"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID280"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID281"}],"Options":{"BlockLocking":false,"RandomizeQuestions":"Advanced","Randomization":{"Advanced":{"FixedOrder":["QID274","QID275","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}"],"RandomizeAll":["QID277","QID278","QID279","QID280","QID281","QID276"],"RandomSubSet":[],"Undisplayed":[],"TotalRandSubset":0,"QuestionsPerPage":0},"EvenPresentation":false},"BlockVisibility":"Expanded","Looping":"Static","LoopingOptions":{"Static":{"1":{"1":"a lot that  life goes on and things are possible"},"2":{"1":"it is a nice research."},"3":{"1":"The leson learnd is the one should always be willing to take risk for the further is unknown. "},"4":{"1":"I have learnt that its important to keep up with the current real time statistics and then try to use them to project the future especially in business its important to keep up with the trends for example now day everyone is talking AI, so its important to recognise current trends."}},"Randomization":"Subset","TotalRandSubset":"1"}}},"39":{"Type":"Standard","SubType":"","Description":"message bike","ID":"BL_emq3wVDboKFROsK","BlockElements":[{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID282"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID283"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID284"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID285"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID286"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID287"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID288"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID289"}],"Options":{"BlockLocking":false,"RandomizeQuestions":"Advanced","Randomization":{"Advanced":{"FixedOrder":["QID282","QID283","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}"],"RandomizeAll":["QID285","QID286","QID287","QID288","QID289","QID284"],"RandomSubSet":[],"Undisplayed":[],"TotalRandSubset":0,"QuestionsPerPage":0},"EvenPresentation":false},"BlockVisibility":"Expanded","Looping":"Static","LoopingOptions":{"Static":{"1":{"1":"it wasnt really that useful to me cause that's something I hardly research or be keen to know"},"2":{"1":"I learnt that when packaging something, if you highlight that it's fragile via packaging means, the shipping provider will be more likely to take greater care when handling the package, resulting in less damage."},"3":{"1":"that companies make packaging appear fragile so it'll be taken care of better"},"4":{"1":"The information was about packing items for shipping in such a way that it appears as a fragile item and that can reduce the damage to the item to a great extent."},"5":{"1":"Whoever transports the product from the business to the costumer might treat the product with extra care if a \"Fragile\" symbol is displayed in the box. This could possibly decrease the chance of the product not being delivered in the intended conditions"},"6":{"1":"Using packaging that looks like it contains fragile stuff, or says that it contains fragile items. makes people more careful with it. It is true probably but it doesn't seem very useful to package something with instructions on how to handle it. As such instructions seem to be seldomly followed. "},"7":{"1":"It's not really provided much insight into packaging. I already knew how to do something safely."}},"Randomization":"Subset","TotalRandSubset":"1"}}},"40":{"Type":"Standard","SubType":"","Description":"relevant bike","ID":"BL_1STt2QEMkNjjtTE","BlockElements":[{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID290"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID291"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID292"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID293"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID294"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID295"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID296"},{"Type":"Question","QuestionID":"QID297"}],"Options":{"BlockLocking":false,"RandomizeQuestions":"Advanced","Randomization":{"Advanced":{"FixedOrder":["QID290","QID291","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}","{~Randomized~}"],"RandomizeAll":["QID293","QID294","QID295","QID296","QID297","QID292"],"RandomSubSet":[],"Undisplayed":[],"TotalRandSubset":0,"QuestionsPerPage":0},"EvenPresentation":false},"BlockVisibility":"Expanded","Looping":"Static","LoopingOptions":{"Static":{"1":{"1":"Some companies use strategies that may deceive customers as well, the fact that the package would have a wrong product on the outside is very wrong and deceiving."},"2":{"1":"I learned that you can manipulate a situation for a better outcome."},"3":{"1":"I have learnt  that anything  that is fragile  and needs to be transported  has to be marked fragile  so that it is easy for transporters to know what they are dealing with"}},"Randomization":"Subset","TotalRandSubset":"1"}}},"41":{"Type":"Standard","SubType":"","Description":"irrelevant bike","ID":"BL_8eNlkUnqE8eTMTI","BlockElements":[{"