ny decided to make their shipping boxes look like they held a television, which is re...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"A bike company decided to make their shipping boxes look like they held a television, which is relatively fragile. This may have reduced damages due to shipping by 80%.","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"sp.wwt","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"A bike company decided to make their shipping boxes look like they held a television, which is re...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID12"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_bs9iO73rCNapKB0","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID9","SecondaryAttribute":"A bike company made their shipping boxes look like they contained a television, which is relative...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"A bike company made their shipping boxes look like they contained a television, which is relatively fragile. In turn, damages caused by shipping were reduced by 80%.","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"sd.wwt","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"A bike company made their shipping boxes look like they contained a television, which is relative...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID9"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_bs9iO73rCNapKB0","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID133","SecondaryAttribute":"After reading, please rate the following just based on the message (the blue text).","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<b>After reading, please rate the following just based on the message<\/b> (<span style=\"color:#2980b9;\"><i>the blue text<\/i><\/span>).","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Q133","QuestionID":"QID133","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"After reading, please rate the following just based on the message (the blue text).","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1}},{"SurveyID":"SV_bs9iO73rCNapKB0","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID161","SecondaryAttribute":"After reading, please rate the following just on the message again (the blue text). You are welco...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<b>After reading, please rate the following just on the message again<\/b> (<span style=\"color:#2980b9;\"><i>the blue text<\/i><\/span>). You are welcome to give the same answers or change them as you see fit.","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"After reading, please rate the following just on the message again (the blue text). You are welco...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"Please rate the following just based on the message (the blue text).","DataExportTag":"Q161","QuestionID":"QID161"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_bs9iO73rCNapKB0","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID129","SecondaryAttribute":"Again, in a previous study, we had participants review a business lesson and then summarize it in...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<b>Again, in a previous study, we had participants review a business lesson and then summarize it in their own words. Please read and rate what they wrote.<\/b>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Q129","QuestionID":"QID129","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Again, in a previous study, we had participants review a business lesson and then summarize it in...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1}},{"SurveyID":"SV_bs9iO73rCNapKB0","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID210","SecondaryAttribute":"Again, in a previous study, we had participants review a business lesson and then summarize it in...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<b>Again, in a previous study, we had participants review a business lesson and then summarize it in their own words. Please read and rate what they wrote.<\/b>","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Again, in a previous study, we had participants review a business lesson and then summarize it in...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"<b>Please read the following information:<\/b><br>","DataExportTag":"Q210","QuestionID":"QID210","QuestionJS":"Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnload(function() {\n    \/\/ Define your list of items\n    var itemList = [\n        \"It made me realize i can influence the way people treat my packages by making them seem more fragile than they actually are\",\n        \"That packing carefully your items makes your shipping more safe so that it doesnt break anything\",\n        \"If you pack your delivery in a package resembling a fragile delivery, then it's more likely that your package won't be damaged because people will deal with it more carefully\",\n        \"Use more fragile materials to package the product\",\n        \"This is an easy way to save some money\",\n        \"I learned that packaging that portrays fragileness tends to have a less likelihood of being damaged\",\n        \"I learned that by making a package appear as fragile cargo I could make delivery companies more careful with my packages\",\n        \"I have taken from the lesson that because the packaging would give the impression of being fragile, it will be handled with better care, hence resulting in less damage to said products\",\n        \"Interesting information however limited. could have done with a little more information to make it really useful\",\n        \"I learnt by packaging something up to look like there is something fragile inside greater care is likely to be taken with the package\",\n        \"I learned that the way of package influence how much the products are safe\",\n        \"Packing products into boxes that resemble the ones used for transporting fragile cargo reduces the risk of damage during transportation\",\n        \"To make sure the product doesnt get damage during the transportation fase, companies use tactics such as labeling their goods as fragile in order for them to be treated carefully\",\n        \"Companies that sending stuff are using labels to avoid damages\",\n        \"Using a safer package could help you minimize losses in your business (probably because the product would be less likely to be damaged). This information could be useful if you are planning to start a business in which you plan to send a lot of packages. Otherwise, it doesn't seem that important\",\n        \"Learned about packaging of items in an appropriate way, making sure they are well protected so they won\u2019t get damaged easily and won\u2019t damage the way they are crated up for shipping, and so they can\u2019t damage the tire of haulage that are shipping them\",\n        \"I think that this kind of information is somewhat valuable, because even if I don't work in this kind of context, in some moment of my life I could use this information later in my life\"\n];\n\nvar randomIndex = Math.floor(Math.random() * itemList.length);\nQualtrics.SurveyEngine.setEmbeddedData(\"message\", itemList[randomIndex]);\n\t});"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_bs9iO73rCNapKB0","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID220","SecondaryAttribute":"Again, in a previous study, we had participants review a business lesson and then summarize it in...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<b>Again, in a previous study, we had participants review a business lesson and then summarize it in their own words. Please read and rate what they wrote.<\/b>","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Again, in a previous study, we had participants review a business lesson and then summarize it in...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"<b>In a previous study, we had participants review some information and then summarize it in their own words. Please read and rate what they wrote.<\/b>","QuestionJS":"Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnload(function() {\n    \/\/ Define your list of items\n    var itemList = [\n        \"It made me realize i can influence the way people treat my packages by making them seem more fragile than they actually are\",\n        \"That packing carefully your items makes your shipping more safe so that it doesnt break anything\",\n        \"If you pack your delivery in a package resembling a fragile delivery, then it's more likely that your package won't be damaged because people will deal with it more carefully\",\n        \"Use more fragile materials to package the product\",\n        \"This is an easy way to save some money\",\n        \"I learned that packaging that portrays fragileness tends to have a less likelihood of being damaged\",\n        \"I learned that by making a packag