omIndex]);\n\t});","DataExportTag":"Q220","QuestionID":"QID220"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_bs9iO73rCNapKB0","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID228","SecondaryAttribute":"Again, in a previous study, we had participants review a business lesson and then summarize it in...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<b>Again, in a previous study, we had participants review a business lesson and then summarize it in their own words. Please read and rate what they wrote.<\/b>","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Again, in a previous study, we had participants review a business lesson and then summarize it in...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"<b>In a previous study, we had participants review some information and then summarize it in their own words. Please read and rate what they wrote.<\/b>","QuestionJS":"Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnload(function() {\n    \/\/ Define your list of items\n    var itemList = [\n        \"It made me realize i can influence the way people treat my packages by making them seem more fragile than they actually are\",\n        \"That packing carefully your items makes your shipping more safe so that it doesnt break anything\",\n        \"If you pack your delivery in a package resembling a fragile delivery, then it's more likely that your package won't be damaged because people will deal with it more carefully\",\n        \"Use more fragile materials to package the product\",\n        \"This is an easy way to save some money\",\n        \"I learned that packaging that portrays fragileness tends to have a less likelihood of being damaged\",\n        \"I learned that by making a package appear as fragile cargo I could make delivery companies more careful with my packages\",\n      